remarks.format: ## Remarks 在原始元数据，这将编码为任一 ELEMENT_TYPE_CLASS (0x12) 对于引用类型和 ELEMENT_TYPE_VALUETYPE (0x11) 对于值类型。In raw metadata, this will be encoded as either ELEMENT_TYPE_CLASS (0x12) for reference types and ELEMENT_TYPE_VALUETYPE (0x11) for value types. 因为 Windows 运行时投影的项目可以从类到值类型或进行相反转换和原始代码有误导性在这些情况下，这被折叠到单一的代码。This is collapsed to a single code because Windows Runtime projections can project from class to value type or vice-versa and the raw code is misleading in those cases.
